Achievements.Name: Welcome to HQ
Achievements.Description: Launch the game for the first time.

Achievements.Name: First Party
Achievements.Description: Start a game mode for several players.

Achievements.Name: Big party
Achievements.Description: Start a game mode for 16 players.

Achievements.Name: Minor squaddie
Achievements.Description: Get 1 star in a game.

Achievements.Name: Sergeant Major
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars in a game.

Achievements.Name: Colonel Major
Achievements.Description: Get 1 star in all games.

Achievements.Name: Major-General
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars in all games.

Achievements.Name: King of TP
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 20,000 TP DollarZ in your kitty.

Achievements.Name: TP Emperor
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 50,000 TP DollarZ for your kitty.

Achievements.Name: 1 Kilo-rab-Bit
Achievements.Description: Hit, flatten or make 1,024 Rabbids explode in the various games.

Achievements.Name: 5 Kilo-rab-Bits
Achievements.Description: Hit, flatten or make 5,120 Rabbids explode in the various games.

Achievements.Name: 10 Kilo-rab-Bits
Achievements.Description: Hit, flatten or make 10,240 Rabbids explode in the various games.

Achievements.Name: Marathon
Achievements.Description: Play for 2 hours, 3 minutes and 59 seconds in one session.

Achievements.Name: Round the clock
Achievements.Description: Clock up 24 hours of total play time.

Achievements.Name: Still at it?
Achievements.Description: Play 6 months after your first game.

Achievements.Name: Insomniac
Achievements.Description: The name says it all.

Achievements.Name: Social netnerd
Achievements.Description: Upload a photo to the Rabbids site.

Achievements.Name: You're completely Uplay
Achievements.Description: Launch Uplay and sign up.

Achievements.Name: Show-off
Achievements.Description: Do 100 headbutts in Rabbzilla.

Achievements.Name: Olé!
Achievements.Description: In Hot Dogs in Danger, let all the Rabbids through without leaving the play space.

Achievements.Name: Udder slapper
Achievements.Description: In the Slapping Station game, slap 4 cows during a game.

Achievements.Name: Ibiza
Achievements.Description: Make the Rabbids dance in Life's a Beach.

Achievements.Name: Thank you, friend!
Achievements.Description: In the Rabbid-o-matic game, get the Rabbid to the end without it falling into a trap.

Achievements.Name: Pump 'n' Pose
Achievements.Description: Do 200 successful poses in Pumped Up.

Achievements.Name: Six machine
Achievements.Description: In the Big Brother game, play as a team of 6 players.

Achievements.Name: Snotput slinger
Achievements.Description: During Snot Funny, steal the snot from the other player.

Achievements.Name: Talk to the hand
Achievements.Description: In the Whack a Rabbid game, smash a Rabbid with your hand.

Achievements.Name: Flaming friends
Achievements.Description: In the Flaming balls of fire game, earn 180 points during a rally against another player.

Achievements.Name: Psycho
Achievements.Description: Successfully make 90 shapes in Silhou-wet.

Achievements.Name: Slashed prices
Achievements.Description: In the Crazy Sales game, fire at all the special offer signs on the sides.

Achievements.Name: Lumberjack
Achievements.Description: Saw through 90 blocks in Hacked Off!

Achievements.Name: Cinderella
Achievements.Description: In the Sauce Wars game, mop up the floor with your hands.

Achievements.Name: Showbiz star
Achievements.Description: Let all the spotlights hit you in Now You See Me

Achievements.Name: Copycow
Achievements.Description: Get 100 moves right in Udder Nonsense.

Achievements.Name: Hop you can do it
Achievements.Description: Play an entire game of Tenderfoot Dance on just one foot.

Achievements.Name: Super sushi
Achievements.Description: Jump 120 times in Salmon Rush Day.

Achievements.Name: No mean feet!
Achievements.Description: In Rabbids-in-the-Hole, play using your feet.

Achievements.Name: Rock Star
Achievements.Description: Finish Guitar Zero with 35 correctly played notes in a row.

Achievements.Name: Super Suppository
Achievements.Description: In Inner Journey, maintain maximum speed for 20 seconds.

Achievements.Name: They help you see in the dark
Achievements.Description: In Carrot Juice, drink 10 glasses in infinite mode.

Achievements.Name: Jackpot
Achievements.Description: In The Kitty game mode, bank the highest possible amount.

Achievements.Name: Harakiri
Achievements.Description: In Forfeits!, get 100% negative opinions for a forfeit.

Achievements.Name: You should take a break
Achievements.Description: Chalk up 100 failures in the cartoon games.

Achievements.Name: Break the piggy bank
Achievements.Description: Buy something in My Raving Rabbid.

Achievements.Name: Spendthrift
Achievements.Description: Buy everything in My Raving Rabbid.

Achievements.Name: Monkey!
Achievements.Description: In My Raving Rabbid, take a photo while doing a pose.

Achievements.Name: Missing
Achievements.Description: In My Raving Rabbid, stay out of the sensor's line of sight for 30 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Babysitter
Achievements.Description: In My Raving Rabbid, find 7 different ways to interact with the Rabbid without using an object.

Achievements.Name: Pacifist
Achievements.Description: In My Raving Rabbid, don't hit the Rabbid for 2 minutes.

Achievements.Name: Close-up
Achievements.Description: In My Raving Rabbid, take a photo of the Rabbid that crashes into your screen.
